Trudeau&#39;s &quot;personality has collapsed&quot;, can he still be re-elected?
The &quot;big hole&quot; that caused Trudeau to stumble this time was dug out bit by bit by Trudeau himself.
Recently, Canadian media have exposed many old photos of the current Prime Minister Trudeau, in which Trudeau dressed himself as a black man.
This was considered an obvious act of racial discrimination and immediately caused an uproar in Canada.
After the incident, Trudeau repeatedly apologized to the public.
However, Canadians don’t buy it very much.
Trudeau shot himself in the foot.
As political commentator Riley and others have pointed out, since the &quot;anti-blackface movement&quot; emerged in the United States, Trudeau and the federal Liberal Party have been high-profile in accusing the opposition or dissidents within the party of &quot;making major mistakes&quot; in this regard. &quot; and repeatedly threatened that &quot;whoever makes this mistake should be fired immediately.&quot;
To put it simply, the &quot;big hole&quot; that tripped Trudeau out of trouble this time was exactly what Trudeau dug out bit by bit.
Trudeau is the son of former Canadian Prime Minister Pierre Trudeau. He is young and handsome. When he first debuted, he became a &quot;political idol&quot;.
Originally a &quot;political amateur&quot;, after taking over as leader of the federal Liberal Party, he fought an unexpectedly good battle in the 2015 Canadian federal legislative election - the federal Liberal Party won more than half of the seats in the federal House of Commons and gained the precious right to form a separate government. .
At that time, Trudeau proposed many inspiring political platforms and concepts, such as &quot;ethnic and gender equality&quot;, &quot;ecological environmental protection&quot; and &quot;economic revitalization&quot;, and emphasized the elimination of corruption and &quot;unhealthy practices&quot;.
However, in the five years since he took office, he has failed to make ends meet in almost all the above-mentioned aspects.
Take the issue of &quot;ethnic and gender equality&quot; as an example. Putting aside this &quot;blackface&quot; incident, he has previously paid lip service to a series of issues related to aboriginal people, which has made it difficult for aboriginal groups and leaders to establish a country in Canada. On the 150th anniversary, the protest tent was moved to the gate of the Capitol.
In terms of eradicating corruption, at the end of last year and the beginning of this year, Trudeau was involved in the highly publicized &quot;Lavalin incident.&quot;
It was revealed that he put pressure on the departments and officials responsible for the investigation and asked the latter to &quot;show their favor&quot; in a major violation of laws and regulations and malpractice at the construction engineering company &quot;Lavalin&quot; in his hometown.
Moreover, when the matter escalated, Trudeau turned his anger on the official who disclosed the fraud—the aforementioned Wang Chaudi was the first to disclose the fraud and the then Attorney General of Canada who directly handled the case.
Although there are still doubts about the case itself, the suspicion is difficult to eliminate.
Many observers pointed out that the collapse of Trudeau&#39;s personality during the five years he was in power was mainly caused by his own &quot;digging holes&quot;, and the biggest &quot;holes&quot; are &quot;anticlimactic&quot;, &quot;reaping one&#39;s own consequences&quot; and &quot;being lenient in disciplining oneself but strict in disciplining others&quot;. Three.
Canada&#39;s most authoritative Angus Read poll data shows that since 2015, the number of respondents who support Trudeau has dropped from more than 60% to more than 30%, while those who oppose him have soared from less than 30% to 60%. %above.
Although other opposition parties and their leaders have also performed poorly, even a considerable number of voters who are still willing to vote for the federal Liberal Party now disapprove of the personality of the federal prime minister and leader of the ruling party.
On October 21, the new Canadian federal legislative election is about to begin. Can Trudeau repeat his resounding victory five years ago?
The answer may be one word: difficult.
Whether it is from the perspective of corporate competition, consumer experience, or regional aviation integration and Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei development integration, it has far-reaching impact and positive significance.
On September 25, Beijing Daxing International Airport was officially opened to flights.
A reporter from the Beijing News learned from the Beijing Municipal Development and Reform Commission that the Capital Airport is already in a super-saturated operation state, and the opening of Daxing International Airport will enhance the Capital’s aviation service capabilities.
After Shanghai, Beijing has become the second city in my country to have two airports in the same city. Similar to Shanghai Hongqiao International Airport, which mainly serves domestic aviation affairs, and Pudong Airport, which mainly serves international aviation, the Capital Airport and Daxing Airport will also operate in the future. Serve the differentiated positioning of different domestic and international aviation businesses and provide more segmented services.
The opening of Daxing Airport will have a more positive impact on Capital Airport from a business development perspective.
The passenger throughput of Capital Airport exceeded 100 million in 2018, ranking first in the country. However, compared with the rapidly growing business demand, there is still a significant capacity gap, especially there is a large gap in demand for international routes.
In order to better serve the needs of domestic and foreign passengers for tourism and business trips, and to adapt to the urban development trend of Beijing becoming increasingly open and in line with international standards, Daxing International Airport is positioned as a large international hub airport, and plans to meet the annual passenger throughput of 100 million passengers, cargo and mail throughput in the future The volume is 4 million tons.
Therefore, the positioning of the two airports does not overlap, they each target different customer groups, and both have sufficient market space.
From an economic account level, the opening of Daxing International Airport will obviously create a win-win effect, easing the tight situation in Beijing’s aviation capacity, accelerating the growth rate of passenger and cargo throughput, and creating an incremental cake for Capital Airlines’ dual-core operations.
From a user perspective, with the opening of Daxing International Airport, travel in the future does not have to be concentrated at the Capital Airport. It can also reduce a series of problems caused by over-concentration of routes, such as longer transit guarantee time and slower passenger boarding speed. , which indirectly increases the detention time of aircraft and passengers at the airport and increases the burden on airport operations. By reducing the shipping burden at Capital Airport, it actually improves the travel experience of passengers.
According to media calculations on the time and cost of various transportation routes to large international airports, if you start from the South Fifth Ring Road and take the Beijing-Kaifeng Expressway and go directly to the Daxing Airport Expressway, you can get there in 50 minutes by car, and the gas cost is about 40 yuan for a round trip, and the expressway fee 15 yuan; if you choose the rail transit subway Daxing Airport Line, the distance is limited to 20 kilometers or 30 kilometers according to the distance, and the fares are divided into three levels: 10 yuan, 25 yuan, and 35 yuan; citizens can also take the Beijing-Xiongan intercity bus from Beijing It only takes more than 20 minutes from West Railway Station to Daxing Airport Station.
Generally speaking, citizens have a variety of transportation options to choose from to go to Daxing Airport, and the cost and time are also within a reasonable range.
From the perspective of trend development: Daxing Airport is positioned as a transportation hub in the Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei region, so it is slightly far away from the urban area of Beijing. However, it has strengthened its radiation to Hebei and Tianjin, making it easier for more people to travel, and it will stimulate the economy of Hebei and Tianjin. Development is of great significance.
In the future, passengers from Hebei and Tianjin can enjoy more international air route services provided by Daxing International Airport, which is evident from the transportation planning of Daxing Airport.
The supporting transportation facilities of Daxing Airport are very complete. In addition to the new airport line directly from Beijing city to Daxing Airport, there are also a number of expressways connecting Daxing Airport and surrounding areas.
Just like passengers from cities such as Dongguan, Foshan, and Qingyuan in Guangdong can go to Guangzhou Baiyun Airport through the Guangzhou-Foshan Expressway and Guangzhou-Shenzhen Expressway, residents in Langfang, Xiongan New Area and other places around Beijing will also benefit from Daxing Airport and obtain convenient and efficient aviation services. Serve.
It can be seen from this that the opening of Daxing International Airport is not just about adding a few runways and a few planes, whether it is from the perspective of corporate competition, consumer experience, regional aviation integration, and Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei development integration It has far-reaching impact and positive significance at all levels. It is not only related to the long-term layout and development of Beijing&#39;s shipping industry, but also provides diversified travel choices for the majority of residents in Beijing, Tianjin and Hebei, promotes the further improvement of the service quality of Beijing&#39;s shipping industry, and is more conducive to the promotion of Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei It is hoped that the integrated development process of Hebei will stimulate the economic and trade development of the areas surrounding Daxing Airport.
Therefore, regarding the navigation of Daxing Airport, we must not only consider the small accounts of individuals economically, but also the big accounts of overall development.
