Thanks to the heart-warming technology of &quot;Internet + Smart Stop Signs&quot;, Nanjing citizens have realized convenient and efficient public transportation such as &quot;checking the bus location before going out, knowing the arrival time when waiting for the bus, and knowing the arrival time at the destination when taking the bus.&quot; Travel mode.
