In order to alleviate the lag and congestion of vehicles on the North and South Roads of South Station, Guangzhou South Railway Station will open three new parking lots, adding 1,000 parking spaces, and alleviate the pressure of poor traffic around South Station.
Shenzhen North Railway Station will open a &quot;high-speed rail-subway&quot; inspection-free green channel.
From October 6th to 7th, when passenger flow reaches peak hours, the A2 exit of Shenzhen North Railway Station will be connected to the subway, and an inspection-free passage will be set up to facilitate travel for passengers arriving during peak hours.
In addition, U-color love express lanes will be regularly set up in East and West Plazas to serve passengers who arrive at the station 15 minutes before driving and special key passengers.
The Guangzhou-Kowloon Passenger Transport Section carried out all-staff business training on the eve of the National Day Golden Week to ensure that all train crew members learn and master business knowledge, improve service quality, and ensure that train crew members can fulfill their respective responsibilities with a good spirit and more professional standards. One trip to provide passengers with better services.
